<style>
  .multicol {
    column-count: 2;
    column-fill: auto;
    column-gap: 0px;
    height: 100px;
    width: 100px;
    margin-left: -100px;
  }
  .rel {
    position: relative;
  }
  .abs {
    position: absolute;
    width: 50px;
    height: 200px;
    background: red;
    transform: translateX(0);
  }
  .fixed {
    position: fixed;
    width: 50px;
    height: 200px;
    top: 0px;
    background: green;
  }
</style>
<p><p>Test passes if there is a filled green square and <strong>no red</strong>.</p></p>
